These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-1::.
There 2 different types of food: pineapple, peach
House: futuristic, townhouse
1. the person eating peach is somewhere to the left of the futuristic house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Food           | peach | pineapple |
| House   | townhouse     | futuristic  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, almond-milk
There 2 different types of food: pineapple, raspberry
1. the person eating pineapple is somewhere to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |
| Beverage         | almond-milk   | soy-milk      |
| Food   | pineapple | raspberry |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, cola
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: october, may
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in october##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2    |
| Beverage   | cola | hot-chocolate    |
| Birthday     | october | may |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-4::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: biathlon, snowboarding
2 different pets are kept: turtle, mouse
1. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |
| Sport   | biathlon   | snowboarding |
| Pet   | turtle | mouse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-5::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: may, july
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, bluemaster
1. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere to the right of the bluemaster-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |
| Birthday   | july | may |
| Cigar     | bluemaster    | dunhill    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-6::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: zombie, western
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: zinnia, begonia
1. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere to the right of the person who growszinnia##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |        2        |
| Movie-Genre   | western  | zombie     |
| Flower        | zinnia | begonia |

