.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-16::.
2 different pets are kept: frog, guinea-pig
The people use 2 different means of transport: tram, snowmobile
1. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere to the left of the owner of the frog##5
2. the owner of the frog is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |
| Pet      | guinea-pig        | frog  |
| Transport   | snowmobile | tram |

